OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMorning showers clearing to
OL,6,Fleave a mainly dry and bright day,
OL,7,Fwith some sunny spells developing at
OL,8,Ftimes. Cloud thickening by late
OL,9,Fafternoon, with drizzle possible over
OL,10,Fthe Cumbrian hills. Turning breezy
OL,11,Fhere too.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA wet and windy evening as
OL,14,Frain spreads southwards. The rain
OL,15,Fheavy at times but generally clearing
OL,16,Fduring the early hours. Gales possible
OL,17,Faround the coasts and over the hills.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
