OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA bright and breezy day.
OL,6,FGenerally dry, with sunny spells but
OL,7,Fthe odd light shower may drift in on
OL,8,Fthe fresh northwesterly breeze.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FFine on
OL,11,FFriday, with pleasant spells of
OL,12,Fsunshine. Cloudier on Saturday, with
OL,13,Fperhaps some light rain over the hills
OL,14,Fat times. Warmer and brighter again on
OL,15,FSunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
